# otelPRE
minut += 30
clr
gs 'statPRE'
fcolor = rgb(0, 0, 0)
bcolor = rgb(255, 255, 255)
lcolor = rgb(106, 90, 205)
money -= 3000
'<center><img src="images/picPRE/otelPRE.jpg"></center>'
'Your trip to the Hotel is quite uneventful compared to your tomb raiding spiel. You park your car go to the receptionist to get a room.'
'There are only double rooms available, but you since your company is paying for your stay, you don''t really seem to care. You take your key and go to your room.'

act 'Up to the room.':
	cla
	*clr
	minut += 5
	clr
	gs 'statPRE'
	'<center><img src="images/picPRE/otelPRE1.jpg"></center>'
	'You lay down on one of the beds and start to wonder who built that crypt and what it''s purpose was. You also think about that amulet you''ve found, the fact that you touched it half an hour ago, but you still feel wonderful, baffles you.'

	act 'Call the director.':
		cla
		*clr
		minut += 30
		clr
		gs 'statPRE'
		'<center><img src="images/picPRE/otelPRE1.jpg"></center>'
		'You decide to dial Roman''s number and after a few rings, he picks up. You told him the details of what you found at the site with Igor: the ancient tomb, human bones, the scrolls in a mysterious language and the altar in that room.'
		'The director keeps silent, while you tell him all about it... then he decides it would be best to stop the construction. He tells you to stay and over the site until further notice.'
		'You put the phone away. <i>Looks like this journey is going to be longer than expected</i>, you think to yourself.'

		act 'Go to bed.':
			cla
			*clr
			minut += 600
			clr
			gs 'statPRE'
			'<center><img src="images/picPRE/otelPRE1.jpg"></center>'
			'It doesn''t take you long to drift into sleep'
			'Visions begin to form in your mind and soon you find yourself in a middle of a dream. You see the amulet in front of you and out comes a ghost of some sort. Before realizing you find yourself staring deep into the ghost''s eyes as it reflects a moon.'
			'"Look at the world. People see the world, but not as it really is."'
			'Suddenly you feel the motel room around you in your dream, but you are not alone.'

			act 'Open your eyes.':
				cla
				*clr
				minut += 5
				clr
				gs 'statPRE'
				'<center><img src="images/picPRE/tobiPRE.jpg"></center>'
				'As you open your eyes, you see a black figure standing in your room. He wears a long black coat and a strange orange mask on his face; the mask only had a single one hole for the eyes.'
				'He approaches you, "Where is the amulet?"'

				act 'Who are you?':
					cla
					*clr
					minut += 5
					clr
					gs 'statPRE'
					'<center><img src="images/picPRE/tobiPRE.jpg"></center>'
					'"Who are you?" you ask puzzled. The man''s sudden appearence and dress feels out of this world.'
					'"Listen, don''t cause any probles now, give me the amulet, close the construction site and all be fine. After all that place belongs to us," the stranger said in a firm voice.'
					'Belongs to us? His response leaves you bewildered, wondering who he is and what this is all about.'
					'"Well, how about I give you a small taste of my power." the man said, and out of nowhere you feel a burning desire to give him the amulet.'

					act 'Give him the amulet':
						cla
						*clr
						minut += 5
						clr
						gs 'statPRE'
						'<center><img src="images/picPRE/otelPRE1.jpg"></center>'
						'You get out of the bed and give him the statue, you had put in your pants earlier. The man takes it, steps back and then without a warning, you see something in his single eye begin to spin like a whirlwind, causing your eyes to blur as if the mask somehow spins with it. A few seconds later your vision clears and the man somehow disappeared into thin air.' 
						'You rub your eyes, "What the hell is going on here? Was that a dream?. No, can''t be, I wouldn''t walk around in a dream. I think." You check your pants, the amulet is indeed gone. You sit down on the bed trying to make sense of what just happened.'
						'Lost in thought, you hear a knock on the door. You get up to get to the door, you aren''t expecting visitors this late at night.'
						'"...who''s there?", you ask, still being a confused.'
						'A woman''s voice responds that she''s the hotels receptionist and she needs to talk to you on an urgent matter.'

						act 'Answer the door':
							cla
							*clr
							minut += 5
							clr
							gs 'statPRE'
							'<center><img src="images/picPRE/karinPRE.jpg"></center>'
							'You open the door, but you don''t remember the woman infront you from the reception desk, the woman from earlier didn''t have red hair and glasses. After entering the room she quickly examines the place, before locking her eyes on you.'
							'"Michael, right?" - You nod.'
							'"Last night you went to a certain place and took out something very valuable and powerful." the woman tells you.'

							act 'Listen, there was already someone like you here.':
								cla
								*clr
								minut += 5
								clr
								gs 'statPRE'
								'<center><img src="images/picPRE/karinPRE.jpg"></center>'
								'<i>Again?</i> You sigh, irritated that not only you''ve been disturbed in the middle of the night, these idiots apparently can not even agree among themselves who is going to disturb you.'
								'"Listen, you''re starting to bother me. That other guy already showed up asking for the damn amulet."'
								'She looks at you with surprise. "What? Someone already came here? Who was it?"'

								act 'Tell her':
									cla
									*clr
									minut += 5
									clr
									gs 'statPRE'
									'<center><img src="images/picPRE/karinPRE.jpg"></center>'
									'"It was some man in a black cloak with red clouds and orange mask with one hole for the eyes. He already took the amulet." you answered.'
									'The girl''s face fell. "Damn it! Okay... Michael, we better have our chat at another place, Juugo, come here." says the girl at the door.'
									'A tall man enters the room'

									act 'Prepare to fight':
										cla
										*clr
										minut += 5
										clr
										gs 'statPRE'
										'<center><img src="images/picPRE/jugoPRE.jpg"></center>'
										'The man has a large tattoo across the left side of his face. He too has red hair'
										$nameV = 'Juugo'
										!!stats
										strenV = 600
										speedV = 60
										agilV = 60
										reactV = 50
										vitalV = 200
										intelV = 50
										willV = 50
										!!skills
										magikV = 100
										boxingV = 100
										shootV = 100
										!!parameters
										healthV = vitalV * 10 + strenV * 5
										mannaV = intelV * 10 + magikV * 10
										willpowerV = willV * 10
										BonusAtakV = 0
										BonusDefV = 0
										!!Programme of Action
										program = 0
										jugoFight = 1

										act 'Fight':gt 'fight', 'start'
									end
								end
							end
						end
					end
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

